      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BEDAZZLED BUDDY (1) is a handy type who was well below best latest at this track, finishing eighth (25.74) in a Grade 4/5. Generally fast into stride but was shuffled back from the tricky draw last time. Solid record here at the distance winning four races. The form out of last race has been strong. Should be very hard to beat this time. IMPRESS SPIETH (8) boasts a strong record this course with nine wins and four minors from 24 tries. Scored by 4 lengths last time (25.12) in a Grade 4/5 over 431m at this track. Can feature with the right run. WALK THE TALK (2) ran below his best last time finishing fifth (17.96) over 324m at Richmond Straight in a NG. Solid record here at the distance winning five races. Has won two of three starts from this draw. Should be about the mark. WARLORD NEV (6) scored last time and appeals as a top-three prospect.",
